---
title: Anushka's Dauphinoise Topped Beef Cottage Pie with Bacon, Carrot and Italian Style Cheese
description: This Anushka's Dauphinoise Topped Beef Cottage Pie is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R10_W14_UK_R12982-5_Main__3low-c116ec01.jpg
